{
  "stem": "802.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But if you didn't have that gumption, if you didn't have that-- that will-- and I think my will came from the fact that I was with my mother and sister because we were like-- we were like one organism.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were literally breathing for one another.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] So we were sent to the punitive barrack.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All three of us, right, because we were-- they were called us 'the monkeys,' because we quarreled about the soup.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And one day-- there were 500 of us in the barracks, three levels high.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we slept in one bunk, the three of us, because there was no straw anymore, and the cold was just unspeakable.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And one day, there was a bit of humming-- you know, people were talking, so there was noise in the barracks.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she constantly screamed, be quiet, be quiet-- you have 500 people in the barrack-- even if you-- if you sneeze, or if you say a word, move or something.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she took me out of the-- and she said, I'm going to give this child-- 24-- I'll whip her 24 times, 25 times.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What is called?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'll give her-- I'll-- with the-- I'll lash her 25 times if there's no absolute silence.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So obviously, the women were absolutely silent, and obviously I was terrified.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But she, in some way, sadistic and terrible as she was, saved my life and my mother's and my sister's, and I will tell you how.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But one day-- again, we were separated.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother and sister were working outside.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was working inside.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A German came from another camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was not an SS man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was wearing civilian clothes.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
